{"tid":54893,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"入得馬場都係名媛！嚴選4大賽馬會VIP大美人！","createTime":"2016-12-26T02:53:24.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-27T05:49:28.000Z","uid":53178,"like":13,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"229289f5c641c16cb4fbff4c58dcbf353a87a418","tid":54893,"uid":53178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T02:53:24.000Z","msg":"去得馬場嘅女人，有兩種，一種係條命生得賤又想發達嘅爛賭閪，另一種就係又elegant又靚嘅名媛級美人！<br />\n<br />\n上次開post，我大美人李嘉欣同大家嚴選咗5個「嘉欣界」美人：<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/39838?ref=ios\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/39838?ref=ios</a><br />\n今次等我同大家再分享幾個經常踏足馬場，不同品種嘅「賽馬會 V I P 大美人」 ！<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">馬場美人之首<br />\n大 美 人 李 嘉 欣！</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n</strong></span><br />\n「最靚港姐」大美人李嘉欣08年同痴心情長劍許晉亨結婚後，生活多姿多釆！對Michele好好的愛馬之人許晉亨，經常帶住省鏡老婆入馬場威！大美人婚後亦成為愛駒「一寶」、「貳寶」、「駟寶」嘅馬主，間唔中仲同老爺許世勳入場，捧撚紅晒許家所有愛駒！大美人每次出場，必定艷壓全場，馬場美人之首，當之無愧！<br />\n<strong><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">恭喜恭喜！<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/26/102545_6b7ab7d786f52ba0791252695428c726.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F26%2F102545_6b7ab7d786f52ba0791252695428c726.jpg&h=ec6f6a81&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wNPD187.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwNPD187.jpg&h=5a4dd18f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kJ3j8PQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkJ3j8PQ.jpg&h=50bfad3b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/26/104345_7c41ba34ad6df65e55b0ced37cbfa2a5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F26%2F104345_7c41ba34ad6df65e55b0ced37cbfa2a5.jpg&h=d3f9862b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://imglf1.nosdn.127.net/img/QzlDT00vNkNTTmdJaGF5SE1VVXdkZmFNNVlQRVhObFkwenhmdUNPeEJlUDBBYnI0aG02NGpRPT0.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimglf1.nosdn.127.net%2Fimg%2FQzlDT00vNkNTTmdJaGF5SE1VVXdkZmFNNVlQRVhObFkwenhmdUNPeEJlUDBBYnI0aG02NGpRPT0.gif&h=0185c6ec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">馬場凍齡美人：吳 婉 芳</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n86年奪港姐亞軍兼最上鏡小姐的吳婉芳，早年同商人胡家驊拍拖7年後結婚，生咗2仔1女。婚後仲不時陪住老公入場撐愛駒。吳婉芳駐顏有術，49歲高齡仍然相當高貴，對腳亦未見出現靜脈曲張，又白又滑，令不少喜歡人妻的網民，幻想能夠一嚐滋味。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/26/102755_4c868bacf2efff8491ab0e74ae08b9be.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F26%2F102755_4c868bacf2efff8491ab0e74ae08b9be.jpg&h=16c64ad6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1JPq7YJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1JPq7YJ.jpg&h=0be181e1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/26/102756_76a9458091bc6c2e78575a9c632566eb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F26%2F102756_76a9458091bc6c2e78575a9c632566eb.jpg&h=2a4524a5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n<strong>馬場非主流美人：郭 羅 桂 珍</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n作為莎莎集團老闆郭少明老婆，郭羅桂珍絕對稱得上係名媛界嘅大家姐！同唔少名媛一樣，因為老公鍾意玩下馬仔，而經常踏足馬場的羅桂珍，每次出場，必定能夠驚艷全場。<br />\n<br />\n最令人歎為觀止，莫過於羅桂珍嘅霸氣名媛頭，將非主流同視覺系發揮得淋漓盡致，散發住陣陣女人味！如果下年grad din想初試熟女造型嘅小妹妹，不妨考慮參考呢個造型，建議大家買一隻較硬身嘅髮泥，同print一張龍珠孫悟空卡通圖片做參考，盡量將頭髮與頭髮間，果種猶如八爪魚一樣的囂張氣焰同蓬鬆感，塑造出來！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/244E3T6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F244E3T6.jpg&h=872e7815&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3p8P9Xk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3p8P9Xk.jpg&h=828bc29c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/26/103308_587bf6b3ce9a97357f626e0da3ef6067.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F26%2F103308_587bf6b3ce9a97357f626e0da3ef6067.jpg&h=f0297b73&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jH8Lpe5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjH8Lpe5.jpg&h=0f3d7414&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>馬場時尚美人：伍 燕 梅</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n講咗咁多因為老公而入馬場嘅美人例子，點少得本身鍾意養馬嘅女中豪傑！<br />\n<br />\n作為「萬事」系列馬主嘅伍燕梅，每逢入馬場，必定著上林林總總的紅色戰衣催谷運情！紅色毛毛fur又好、粉紅小熱褲也好，無一樣難到阿梅、無一樣佢carry唔到！在fashion界行走江湖多年的伍燕梅，講taste講氣質，絕對完勝wyman、豬奴、gem同徐酷刑等時裝殘渣。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/26/103551_0aec670751f98e8ac72394364b78d92a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F26%2F103551_0aec670751f98e8ac72394364b78d92a.jpg&h=7559ddc0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/f301r95.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ff301r95.jpg&h=dbdc2d4b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/My7381Y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMy7381Y.jpg&h=47a24938&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n伍燕梅除咗著衫潮，社交能力亦奇高，贏馬時更會主動向練馬師和馬主們獻吻，睇下佢地幾enjoy<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/26/104117_8d65874af26bc48a4e89c1286e085b8a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F26%2F104117_8d65874af26bc48a4e89c1286e085b8a.jpg&h=fc50a668&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/N62747W.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FN62747W.jpg&h=f5e8a7d9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">號外：<br />\n無得入馬場又唔係美人系列</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">洪 欣：西 女 人</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n</span></strong>"},{"pid":"08177f715f68f1bc2010b0597da709663fd57531","tid":54893,"uid":53178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T03:13:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"afd474d38b20dd042fdb0827b9f4c3a12406f54f","tid":54893,"uid":29311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T06:18:49.000Z","msg":"吳婉芳真係正喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfa1aa62e9c8afffda364c3bf6fdac46bb47768b","tid":54893,"uid":34241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T06:20:18.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>我</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"4dbeb457d0df21839264ebb70eb6b990b2d14ddd","tid":54893,"uid":8048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T06:21:23.000Z","msg":"咪又係.."},{"pid":"6878c674617ca51325914439404051d645005580","tid":54893,"uid":66759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T06:33:38.000Z","msg":"屌你後面兩個玩野呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88c10904be229f8c009004948d339698fe109899","tid":54893,"uid":14503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T06:50:11.000Z","msg":"呢4個一定係吳婉芳"},{"pid":"ffa5807a615573dd52dfd1ea998